    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">NOTE: The 'teleological' aspect of a system that indicates things are done with a purpose.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Intention</rdfs:label>
    <skos:scopeNote rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The 'teleological' aspect of a system that indicates things are done with a purpose.</skos:scopeNote>
